Yesterday, an infection was diagnosed that is linked to an infection identified the day before and after sequencing by deCODE Genetics, it was revealed "a new type of virus that has not been detected here before."
Contact tracing is completed in relation to that infection.
Már points out that this is not a new virus, but the same virus that has spread around the world, i.e., the novel coronavirus SARS-CoV-2.
